    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You touch a creature. The creature is warded against the effects of <em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.nqBDWkVOfcGZt4YU]{faerie fire}, @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.3Lo9boi7P2ro6QV4]{hold person}</em>, and <em>@UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressspells.Item.KPorderofrevenge]{order of revenge}</em> for the duration of the effect, granting them advantage on the saving throw against the effect and a saving throw each round they are affected by the spells. If the warded creature is the focus of <em>@UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.spells.Item.gXtzz9t1DTzJeLr4]{locate creature}</em>, the caster may determine if the affected creature is within 1,000 feet but cannot determine the direction to the target of <em>vagrant’s nondescript cloak</em>. If the creature is already affected by one of the warded spells, then both the effect and <em>vagrant’s nondescript cloak</em> end immediately.<br><em><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong></em> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of third level or higher, you can target +1 creature for each slot level above second.<br>Content licensed under the @UUID[Compendium.koboldpressogl.koboldpressjournal.JournalEntry.KoboldPressOGL00.JournalEntryPage.KoboldPressOGLpg]{Open Game License}",
